{"tid":2101942,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"莎莎員工確診，但公司無出過隔離指引","createTime":"2020-07-10T06:32:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-10T07:48:54.000Z","uid":228439,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"55b8ef43a2c1249fd1a6bf5d7a33d3f2a61381dd","tid":2101942,"uid":228439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T06:32:55.000Z","msg":"你好，我係莎莎其中一個寫字樓員工，我地公司係琴晚發現舖頭同事有確診個案，而聽聞該舖頭同事更係早兩天到寫字樓參加左一個過百人的會議。<br />\n<br />\n但公司到現在都沒有任何消毒及隔離指引。原因據說係因為黑心銀袋夫婦驚所有人都要隔離就冇人番工，所以想則則膊拖幾日就冇左回事，而家寫字樓個個人都中十分擔心，但又唔知可以做咩。"},{"pid":"bdbd4ca651809b46e75a1a768c12ca8e6e265a19","tid":2101942,"uid":204272,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T06:35:10.000Z","msg":"報1823"},{"pid":"cd3222a8a77729e72a861132388ffaa0618ca759","tid":2101942,"uid":219356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T06:38:03.000Z","msg":"如果係真。全公司大擴散<br />\n到時就唔止無人返工<br />\n仲要生意都無得做<br />\n你估啲客唔驚咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f11a6fe0241b65fa50bf375fc5efe6e996379a0","tid":2101942,"uid":68689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bdbd4ca651809b46e75a1a768c12ca8e6e265a19","tid":2101942,"uid":204272,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T06:35:10.000Z","msg":"報1823"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T06:38:17.000Z","msg":"一定要處理<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1efb0ec48a5eceed8d8903e6a292960cae68056b","tid":2101942,"uid":10757,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T06:39:52.000Z","msg":"同老細多d傾計 食下飯 表達下意見先得架ma"},{"pid":"adeb729fb09d2015831bfc07a9f15ccb20ead7fc","tid":2101942,"uid":62837,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T06:40:17.000Z","msg":"抵死啦奴隸啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66b2d15b76363db9ab8b19f9288822d4023e0462","tid":2101942,"uid":174502,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T06:41:27.